edBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"周柏豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1EDYnjG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1EDYnjG.gif&h=bfba29c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2824414d34b2dac018ff3919509c078729e5942b","tid":2364593,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"周柏豪 mewe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1b2123991fdb035d616bc44ca4469835187587","tid":2364593,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f1110b1eecdb75a7570d9a824437d94a9bdbeb","tid":2364593,"uid":135040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dfcae5b169afef6011e031bbe7af6f324bf4b2f8","tid":2364593,"uid":49776,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"周柏豪有微博咪夠駛乜mewe"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"佢有we7<br />\n都冇data 可以俾人再拎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早俾人拎哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"咩阿 之前翻大陸酒店<br />\n佢checkin 時比職員影低護照擺上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d19e1be4f545257d57bef8c1e706fdeb6211eae","tid":2364593,"uid":77180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7449f14e6aa65cae657ee7e7fec58b6a4686037","tid":2364593,"uid":228868,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"3e0c164f790b716a855a7b06c3c1ebaa4b67f428","tid":2364593,"uid":280853,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"51c49b9f4d2dc8af1b51d839d7f8a24fb8808f30","tid":2364593,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"時代越壞，越要學識保護自己，WhatsApp更改私隱條款風波，觸發用戶刪app潮，卓韻芝和王喜都在社交網宣告棄用WhatsApp，卓韻芝留言：「日後Signal或短訊，號碼相同，謝謝！」今早阿芝更撰千字文提出私隱的重要性，「我們面對問題：通訊工具是否安全？若你在通訊工具中說的每一句話，都不安全，隨時被輸出：你能夠接受這事實嗎？如果接受，我們又是誰呢？」<br />\n<br />\n阿芝不點名指有些通訊工具，大家是明白要小心說話，但有些以為比較安全的，能夠直腸直肚講工作進度、某人的不是、工作機密等，如果這空間不再可靠，又為何選擇這工具呢？「反抗，不關於一個指定目標，而是在日常生活裏，你覺得有些事不對頭，不公平，例如WhatsApp內每個訊息、每個audio note、每個contact，你要按 &lsquo;agree&rsquo;，然後送給大公司。若你覺得不對頭，你需要說『不』。只有團結，才有機會對抗大鱷魚。逐步逐步，就由通訊工具做起。」她並多謝助手和製作組等共事者，幫忙轉場去Signal。<br />\n<br />\n而一直敢於發言的王喜，亦在社交網表態將在限期前刪WhatsApp：「2021年2月7日2359時後，將不再回答或發出任何WhatsApp，搵唔到我，就咪L搵我。」網民都留言支持。<br />\n<br />\n群星轉場玩MeWe<br />\n至於WhatsApp的母公司Facebook，因為封鎖特朗普的做法和言論審查，近日用戶亦掀起「社交移民」潮，繼葉蘊儀宣佈撤離Facebook，反抗網絡霸權轉玩MeWe，群星都蜂擁開設MeWe，包括：林家謙、鄭敬基、袁彌明、梁祖堯、雨僑、龍小菌、莊韻澄、阮小儀、Sammy＠Koler、盧巧音、泥鯭、周柏豪、鍾舒漫、孫慧雪、石詠莉、Regen、雷有輝、Anjaylia、Naomi、龔柯允等，今日新鮮加入的少爺占留言：「有個信念好易，行出第一步都唔難，最重要係點樣堅持落去。今時今日，大家可以嚟到呢度，要緊記前人為我哋付出咗好多。」<br />\n<br />\n至於有社交障礙的100毛腦細林日曦，留言指暫時不會開Signal和ＭeＷe，「我還記得每一次有人whatsapp我時，我那油然而生的恐懼，我不想再在signal上經歷多一次...原諒我不社交移民，我想社交放一陣假。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210113/MLZV67FZMZDT3FKYFEVE7LJYL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210113%2FMLZV67FZMZDT3FKYFEVE7LJYL4%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvESVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=7c69cde0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210113%2FMLZV67FZMZDT3FKYFEVE7LJYL4%2F&h=3589bd05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210113/MLZV67FZMZDT3FKYFEVE7LJYL4/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 周柏豪"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"大公報警告: 黃絲轉用Signal及MeWe「播獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2364373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2364373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好去藍絲page講ok?"},{"pid":"e895681457b7106a6c2a380895eb46d5cfa58bf5","tid":2364593,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c8b7c9ea0edb7d022ecc0a6112651757c49d60","tid":2364593,"uid":325757,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比比鳥真係五時花六時變人做佢又做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"吹咩"},{"pid":"07c2be9fff2030f1b28c18c5656d82d374eed60c","tid":2364593,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d4dd26dada4ff1f66b1f9b703266d4417765d7c","tid":2364593,"uid":65556,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"周柏豪係咩一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:24:51.000Z","msg":"上次含完馬戲叻<br />\n照樣俾小粉紅喪屌佢港獨扮愛國<br />\n唔知係咪又想轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee891a3f78895ec4c8e762ef031143f8f8a95a76","tid":2364593,"uid":13067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021